    "Management": {
      "text": "If no signs of chronic process: Medical management (Colchicine, NSAIDs for 2-3 months)\nChronic signs: Anasarca, cachexia,\natrial fibrillation\n, hepatic dysfunction, pericardial calcification\nIf chronic process: Pericardiectomy\n[4]\nDefinitive treatment is surgical pericardiectomy",
